Parterapi 

About the Game
Parterapi is a browser-based Memory / Concentration game for up to 4 players, where players flip cards to find matching pairs. The game features smooth flip animations and an engaging visual experience powered by Three.js.
Flip two cards at a time, remember their positions, and try to match them all using as few attempts as possible.

How It Works
* Game state and logic run on a Node.js server
* The browser handles rendering and user interaction using Three.js
* Communication happens in real time via WebSockets

Prerequisites
Make sure you have Node.js installed.

Installation
1. Clone the repository: 
  git clone <https://github.com/Timalm90/Parterapi/> 
  cd Parterapi
2. Install dependencies: npm install

Running the Application
Start the server:
npm start
Then open your browser and navigate to:
http://localhost:3000
Technology Stack
* Three.js — 3D graphics and rendering
* Node.js — server-side runtime
* WebSocket (ws) — real-time communication between client and server
